    poppatch [-f function] [-m alignment] [-r reference] <-p prefix>

Functions
    coat    Convert an assembly to the coordinates of [-r reference]
    pan     Add assembly data to an existing [-r reference]

Options:
    -f, --function  Process to be performed on the data (see above)
    -h, --help      Prints this message and exits
    -u, --usage     Prints this message and exits
    -m, --map       Mapping data where query data is aligned to the reference. 
                    Accepted formats include: .sam
    -p, --prefix    Prefix of the output file [poppatch].
    -r, --reference Reference that the data has been aligned to. Accepted
                    formats include: .fa, .fna, .fa.gz, .fna.gz, .fasta, 
                    .fasta.gz
    -v, --version   Prints the version information and exits
